      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "你刚把铁盒塞进城隍像后的砖缝里，庙门外忽然传来细碎的脚步声。"
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneSpawnActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_tall_man",
          "name": "高个汉子",
          "x": 520,
          "y": 930
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneSpawnActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_short_man",
          "name": "矮汉子",
          "x": 620,
          "y": 930
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneSpawnActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_woman",
          "name": "女人",
          "x": 570,
          "y": 940
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "parallel",
        "tracks": [
          {
            "kind": "action",
            "type": "moveEntityTo",
            "params": {
              "target": "_cut_temple_woman",
              "x": 580,
              "y": 720,
              "speed": 80
            }
          },
          {
            "kind": "action",
            "type": "moveEntityTo",
            "params": {
              "target": "_cut_temple_tall_man",
              "x": 500,
              "y": 750,
              "speed": 90
            }
          },
          {
            "kind": "action",
            "type": "moveEntityTo",
            "params": {
              "target": "_cut_temple_short_man",
              "x": 660,
              "y": 750,
              "speed": 85
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "你赶紧缩到柱子后头，只听见两个汉子压着嗓子和那女人争执，字句听不真切。"
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "女人",
        "text": "你们到底想做什么！"
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "下一瞬，一声短促的惨叫在空庙里炸开，听得你后背一麻。"
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneRemoveActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_woman"
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneRemoveActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_tall_man"
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "action",
        "type": "cutsceneRemoveActor",
        "params": {
          "id": "_cut_temple_short_man"
        }
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "庙里很快又静了下来。你既想立刻逃走，又实在惦记砖缝里的铁盒还在不在。"
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "cameraMove",
        "x": 910,
        "y": 480,
        "duration": 1200
      },
      {
        "kind": "present",
        "type": "showDialogue",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "你屏住气，往庙门口挪了两步。月光从破屋顶漏下来，斜斜照在墙边……那边似乎有什么。"
      }
    ]
